name: SFBobaApp
0:
”Alexa, open Boba Chooser.”
”Alexa, start Boba Chooser and give me a boba shop.”
”Alexa, ask Boba Chooser where to go for boba.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: boba chooser
des: This quick skill will give you suggestions to some of the best boba, also known as bubble tea, shops in the San Francisco area.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
